For Display:
- MainDisplay class to display the GUI
- There may be other smaller classes (?) to display part of the GUI

For Background Work
- Manager class to receive trigger from GUI, execute functions of other classes and return result for the GUI to display  
- Box class to hold (color or order) value of boxes in the GUI
- BoxCollection class (maybe queue or stack in array or linked list) to hold list of boxes
- Level class (?)
- Saved_Score class (?)
- Report class (?)

